{"tid":1747880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修行左一段時間有感","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T09:02:34.000Z","uid":240250,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39f012a7ad42a0ca890fb6b9c0008e8e449e8e61","tid":1747880,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"第一次見咁多人裝修其實好開心<br />\n覺得呢樣野終於比香港人接受<br />\n終於有少少武力同狗抗衝<br />\n<br />\n但經過幾次大量被示威者使用<br />\n缺點開始浮現<br />\n<br />\n主要係畫面問題<br />\n<br />\n呢一點我知連登好難接受<br />\n但唔好以為唔重要<br />\n裝修舖頭大家都驚都擔心 <br />\n我地可以搬大量同溫層社評去支持自己<br />\n但觀感上國際都會覺得武力升級<br />\n當然咁有好有唔好<br />\n好似美心360既case <br />\n國際見到舖頭變廢墟<br />\n第一時間就諗起趁火打劫<br />\n快速過人權法主要都係因為咁<br />\n但難保下一次裝修出現係其他地方 而我地再控制唔到有人打劫<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家可以停用火魔同裝修，光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"dac8e4c46d8a75baa6b5aa499b25e95f061e857d","tid":1747880,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf30b1093568cd257c8a389bc838a630cb2d58f","tid":1747880,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#240250</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e08a954ef5f571365a2bbe3321194cba6f833bdf","tid":1747880,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"香港人贏左！大家終於可以休息了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}